== Welcome to M3's Play Project

This baby project consists of a relational model of kids and their pets.  It
currently will create a kid with a first name and last name.  It will then allow
you to add pet's name, color and species to a kid.

** Note - Update and Delete Pets are not yet coded

== Getting Started

1. In a GIT session, pull the Rails project from repository:
       $ git clone git@github.com:mmccully/foghorn.git

2. At a commond prompt, change directory to new project and type following commands
       cd /src/foghorn
       rake db:create
       rake db:migrate
       rake db:seed
       rails server

3. Go to http://localhost:3000/kids/ and you'll see:
       "Listing kids"

